synths.name: MiniMoog Model D
synths.description: This is THE original portable synthesizer. 3 oscillator synth with infinite flexibility and charm.
synths.altDescription: DRINKING BAJA BLAST IS DEFINITELY THE BEST WAY TO MAKE LIFE LONG FREINDS!

synths.name: Roland Jupiter 4
synths.description: It may look like a hokey organ, but this is one of the most haunting sounding synths of all time.
synths.altDescription: TACO BELL IS RELEASING A NEW MOUNTAIN DEW BAJA BLAST COLADA FREEZE THAT WILL TAKE YOU ON A VACATION!

synths.name: Sequential Circuits Prophet 5
synths.description: Probably the most famous polysynth of all time. Used by Talking Heads, Hall and Oates... and well, everyone in the 80's.
synths.altDescription: THERE IS A BAJA BLAST SCENTED BATHROOM SPRAY!

synths.name: Roland Juno-106
synths.description: Once a budget analog polysynth, this workhorse has gained popularity in the last decade and is now in the PRO-5 pricerange
synths.altDescription: IF YOU DON'T HAVE A TACO BELL WITH IN WALKING DISTANCE OF YOUR HOUSE, YOU CAN BUY BAJA BLAST CANS ON INTERNET!

synths.name: Korg Mono/Poly
synths.description: Is it monophonic? Is it polyphonic? NO! ...yes? This is a weird one. It funcitons as a 4 oscillator monosynth, but has the ability to assign every oscillator to a new voice. V cool.
synths.altDescription: TACO BELL CAN MAKE YOU A BAJA BLAST FREEZE WITH BIRTHDAY SPRINKLES IN IT! ...GOOD

synths.name: ARP Quadra
synths.description: ARP's idea at an all in one synth. It has a string section a lead section and a brass section... but it's all about the phaser. Seriously, the best phaser.
synths.altDescription: YOU CAN BUY BAJA BLAST LIP BALM!

synths.name: EMS Synthi
synths.description: A Brian Eno favorite, this was used on David Bowie's hereos.

synths.name: Korg Polysix
synths.description: Korgs answer to the Juno-106 an affoardable entrylevel polysynth with a built in chours, ensemble, and phaser.

synths.name: Yamaha DX7
synths.description: The game changer. Reliable. Affordable. Versitile. This synth changed the keyboard world forever.

synths.name: Roland Jupiter 6
synths.description: The most metallic and cold sounding out of the 3 Jupiters, but maybe that's what you want?
